{"article_id":"HCbJzJbZDKy1CZRh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Newly appointed Donald Trump lawyer Rudy Giuliani dropped a bombshell on Wednesday night","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"when he said on Fox News","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that Trump had repaid his attorney Michael Cohen for $ 130,000 in Stormy Daniels hush money .","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Even Sean Hannity ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"who was interviewing Giuliani ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"seemed surprised by the admission .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"It was a shocking moment","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"because it contradicted Trump ' s previous claim","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that he didn ' t know anything about Cohen ' s payment .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The secret payment to the porn actress","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to keep an alleged affair quiet","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"was already a potential legal problem for Trump","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"because it may have violated campaign finance laws .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"If Trump knew about the payment ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and if it was designed to help the campaign","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and it wasn ' t properly disclosed ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"then it ' s illegal .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Before last night ' s revelation , the big question was whether the Daniels payment was technically campaign-related ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"or if it was merely personal .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"If it ' s the former ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Trump is in trouble .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"And if the payment was made","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"without Trump ' s knowledge ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"then he would be off the hook .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"But now we know ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"thanks to Giuliani ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that Trump did know about it","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"- and Trump later confirmed Giuliani ' s account on Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"So what does the legal picture look like for Trump now ?","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"To find out ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"I reached out to 11 legal experts .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Their responses ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"edited for clarity ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"are below .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Giuliani has made things much worse for Trump .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"First , he ' s confirmed that Trump repaid the money ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"meaning Cohen potentially made an unreported loan to the campaign .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"If this was campaign-related ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and Trump failed to report the loan and the repayments of the loan ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that is a campaign finance violation .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"And willful violations can lead to criminal liability .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Much turns on Trump ' s motive .","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"On Fox News , Giuliani suggested","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Trump ' s motivation was indeed campaign-related .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Rudy Giuliani ' s recent comments in interviews seem both unhinged and unhelpful .","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"And in typical fashion , the Trump team appears to be doubling down on his claims in the aftermath .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"At a minimum , Giuliani has flatly contradicted the president ' s earlier statements","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"and exposed his arrangement with Cohen .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"More dangerously , the awkward theory of \" reimbursement \" via retainer fees over time does not solve the problem of an illegal campaign contribution in 2016 .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"It ' s easy to argue","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"when Michael Cohen used $ 130,000 of his own money","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"to pay Stormy Daniels","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"not to reveal her affair with then-candidate Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"that payment was made for a campaign purpose .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"The reasoning is fairly straightforward :","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The payment was made","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"to help Trump ' s campaign","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"because if Daniels revealed the affair ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that would hurt the campaign .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"So Giuliani ' s argument","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that Trump reimbursed Cohen","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"doesn ' t hold up","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"if the payment was still , ultimately , designed to help the campaign .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"This argument is bolstered by the possibility","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that the Trump campaign is paying Michael Cohen ' s legal fees","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"because the payment","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Cohen made to Daniels","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"was related to the campaign .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"So","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"if the payment was indeed made for a campaign purpose ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"then it is a loan to the campaign ,","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"and that is something","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"which must be disclosed and reported to the Federal Election Commission .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"President Trump would also need to disclose and report the repayment .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Failure","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"to report such a loan could be considered to be a false statement .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Also ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"if Trump was repaying Cohen in increments of less than $ 10,000","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"to avoid reporting to the Treasury Department ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"this could be a violation of federal banking laws .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"It ' s called \" illegal structuring , \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"and it ' s the same crime","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that Dennis Hastert was convicted of in 2016 .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Giuliani was not going off script .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"This was a deliberate strategy by Trump and his lawyers ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"now that they know","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Mueller and the Southern District of New York have the financial records","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and that Cohen is probably going to flip","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"- to admit","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"and spin .","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"The problem is that these admissions open up even more legal trouble .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Before last night , Trump ' s official story isolated Cohen for campaign finance and bank fraud felonies .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Now , Trump is on the hook for failing to disclose campaign donations and debts","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"and for conspiring to evade detection with deliberately small reimbursements ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"as Giuliani said ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"\" funneled through a law firm. \"","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"That ' s the language","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"a prosecutor , not a defense attorney , would use","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"to explain illegal activity .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"One overlooked point :","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Giuliani also strengthened the case for obstruction of justice","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"when Trump fired [ FBI Director James ] Comey .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"The official reason was based on Comey ' s handling of Clinton ' s email .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Of course , Trump already told [ NBC News anchor ] Lester Holt and Russian diplomats","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that the real reason was the Russia investigation .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"We know","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Trump told Comey to \" let go \" of [ Michael ] Flynn","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"while admitting","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"that he knew","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Flynn had lied to the FBI .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"But Giuliani further confirmed this corrupt purpose","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"when he said on Fox News","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that Trump \" fired Comey","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"because Comey would not say","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"that he wasn ' t a target of the investigation .","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"He ' s entitled to that .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"Hillary Clinton got that .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"And he couldn ' t get that .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"So he fired him .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"And then he said ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"' I ' m free of this , guys. ' \"","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"This is one more piece of evidence of \" corrupt intent , \" the mental state","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"required by federal obstruction statutes .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"Giuliani ' s comments appear to be part of a strategy","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"to help Michael Cohen ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"who is under investigation for campaign finance violations","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"relating to the Stormy Daniels payment .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Giuliani ' s statements open Trump up to new liability for campaign finance violations and potentially for submitting a false financial disclosure form .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Giuliani and Trump are betting","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that the public won ' t care ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"and Congress won ' t impeach for these potential violations ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"while Cohen remains in the fold .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"All of this begs the question :","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"What does Michael Cohen know ?","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"He must know something important","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"to warrant this kind of exposure from Giuliani and Trump .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"The $ 130,000 payment to Stormy could violate campaign finance laws in a number of ways .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"If the donation is deemed to be a contribution to the candidacy of Mr. Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"then it is way too big .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"At most , Mr. Cohen could give $ 2,700 to Mr. Trump ' s campaign for the general election .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"It also appears to be an unreported contribution ,","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"which is another violation .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Finally , the use of this $ 130,000 could also violate prohibitions on personal use of campaign funds by a federal candidate .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"The rule of thumb with personal use is federal candidates can only use campaign funds for campaign expenditures .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Candidates can ' t do the equivalent","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"of pocketing campaign money","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"or using it","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"to pay for personal things like divorce lawyers .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"What Giuliani ' s admission to Hannity did is provide evidence","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"that Trump had knowledge of the $ 130,000 payment ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"which opens the door not just to legal problems for Mr. Cohen ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"but also to potential legal problems for Trump .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"There is no serious criminal case against Trump for a campaign finance violation","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"relating to the Daniels payoff .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"It would , at most , be a technical violation","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"that no sane prosecutor would base criminal charges on","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"( assuming that such charges could be brought against the president ) .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"Although I have zero sympathy for Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"I am puzzled by the CNN and MSNBC pundits ' apparent unanimity","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"that Giuliani ' s statement","depth":16},{"id":161,"text":"that Trump reimbursed Cohen","depth":16},{"id":162,"text":"was an admission","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"that Trump lied ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"when he previously said","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"he had not known of the Daniels payoff .","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"There is no necessary contradiction here .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"Trump ' s story now is that he knew nothing about the payoff","depth":14},{"id":168,"text":"when it occurred ,","depth":14},{"id":169,"text":"but","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"since it was made on his behalf by his lawyer ,","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"he felt obliged to reimburse Cohen for the payment .","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"If in fact Trump reimbursed Cohen ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"that could only have been hidden for a short time","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"before becoming undeniable .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"I don ' t believe","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"that Giuliani did Trump any serious harm","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"in revealing the reimbursement .","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"Giuliani seemed to enjoy his chats with Fox News on Wednesday evening and Thursday morning .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"Even apart from the unseemly spectacle","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"of watching your lawyer speculate about the state of your marriage on national television ,","depth":14},{"id":181,"text":"no client would want his or her lawyer to highlight even more questions","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"relating to more money from unidentified sources ,","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"thereby fueling even more speculation about a payment","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"made shortly before election day .","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"What did Giuliani mean by his reference","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"to money having been \" funneled \" through a law firm ?","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"Why were reimbursements made in $ 35,000 increments over time ?","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"Giuliani told American voters","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"that $ 130,000 was such a small , insignificant sum","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"that his client could have paid it from his own funds at any time .","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"So why didn ' t he do so ?","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"There was , apparently , far more money than $ 130,000 involved , perhaps an amount","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"approaching $ 500,000 .","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"Where did this come from ?","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"What was it used for ?","depth":15},{"id":196,"text":"What path did it take ?","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"All of this creates new interest in previous suggestions of a fund","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"used to deal with unfortunate behavior by Trump .","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"The only thing","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"Giuliani ' s narrative lacked","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"was an express reference to one or more exempt entities","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"providing nondisclosure and a tax deduction .","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"Perhaps","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"if we stay tuned ,","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"Giuliani will tell us about this as well .","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"The importance of Giuliani ' s admission of repayment is that it indicates","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"Trump and his campaign had knowledge of Cohen ' s hush payment on Trump ' s behalf .","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"Cohen ' s hush payment , for purposes of campaign finance law , might have been a contribution to the Trump campaign","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"even if it were a loan .","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"The Trump campaign would have been required to disclose such a contribution .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"Giuliani ' s admission therefore suggests","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"that Trump and his campaign willfully failed to disclose it ,","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"which could trigger criminal liability under campaign finance law .","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"Having said all that ,","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"the case against Trump for willful failure","depth":14},{"id":216,"text":"to disclose","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"is still not a complete slam-dunk .","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"The circumstances and context here are suspicious ,","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"but it is not entirely clear that Cohen ' s hush payment in fact constitutes a campaign finance contribution .","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"Cohen and Giuliani seem still to maintain","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"that the hush payment was purely personal , not campaign-related ,","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"which remains a gray area in campaign finance law .","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"Giuliani ' s admission , though , concedes","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"that Cohen did not act on his own","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"and acted with Trump ' s understanding .","depth":13},{"id":226,"text":"This not only contradicts Trump ' s earlier positions","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"but also opens the door wider for suspicions about obstruction of justice and use of Trump Organization resources","depth":13},{"id":228,"text":"in facilitating these transactions , among other things .","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"Giuliani ' s comments are obviously inconsistent with what has come before .","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"If the history of this presidency is a guide ,","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"then the latest rendition will last only a few news cycles","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"before it too is clarified into some new version .","depth":9},{"id":233,"text":"All this is exhausting , dispiriting , and bizarre .","depth":8},{"id":234,"text":"But it is not illegal .","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"Presidential confabulation may offend or not ,","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"but it is not constrained by law as such .","depth":8},{"id":237,"text":"Now that we know","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"President Trump authorized the payment during the campaign period ,","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"legal questions do emerge ,","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"despite all the \" nothing to see here \" pronouncements .","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"There are many reasons","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"to suspect","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"that the finances and persona of Trump the individual and Trump the candidate were intertwined ,","depth":11},{"id":244,"text":"just as the separation between the executive branch and the Trump administration has been anything but airtight .","depth":10},{"id":245,"text":"An expenditure of this size at the heart of the campaign raises immediate questions","depth":10},{"id":246,"text":"of where the money came from","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"and how it got paid .","depth":11},{"id":248,"text":"Legally , it makes a difference","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"if it came from Trump himself , or from some private fund of contributions from friends .","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"It makes a difference","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"if the payment through Cohen was funneled through the campaign or privately .","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"Giuliani created some problems","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"in acknowledging","depth":14},{"id":254,"text":"the money trail leads to Trump .","depth":14},{"id":255,"text":"\" Follow the money \" is always a useful guide .","depth":12},{"id":256,"text":"But whether this particular version of events is meaningful , or even around after a day or two , remains to be determined .","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"Last night ' s revelation by Giuliani changes the political landscape much more than the legal one .","depth":8},{"id":258,"text":"The central legal question has not changed :","depth":8},{"id":259,"text":"When Michael Cohen wired $ 130,000 to Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":9},{"id":260,"text":"was he trying to prevent Melania from learning about Clifford ' s allegations","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"or trying to prevent voters in Michigan from hearing these allegations ?","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"Trump ' s acknowledgment","depth":11},{"id":263,"text":"that he was personally involved in the payment","depth":11},{"id":264,"text":"may actually help his legal argument .","depth":10},{"id":265,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":266,"text":"the defense","depth":15},{"id":267,"text":"that this was about protecting Trump ' s marriage","depth":15},{"id":268,"text":"would be very weak","depth":14},{"id":269,"text":"if Michael Cohen had acted alone .","depth":13},{"id":270,"text":"Why would Cohen care about Melania ' s perception of Trump more than Trump himself ?","depth":11},{"id":271,"text":"The Melania defense is much stronger now .","depth":11},{"id":272,"text":"Politically , however , the president of the United States has acknowledged paying hush money to a porn actress","depth":12},{"id":273,"text":"and acknowledged","depth":13},{"id":274,"text":"that he knowingly and willfully lied to the press","depth":14},{"id":275,"text":"when asked about it .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":551,"left":319,"right":550,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":309,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":303,"right":308,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":303,"left":292,"right":302,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":284,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":281,"right":283,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":278,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":0,"right":277,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":277,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":279,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":6,"right":282,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":287,"right":290,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":12,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":285,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":285,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":289,"right":16,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":13,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":302,"left":298,"right":301,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":293,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":294,"right":296,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":295,"right":23,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":295,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":300,"right":27,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":299,"right":26,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":28,"right":307,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":304,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":306,"left":305,"right":33,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":315,"right":317,"relation":"elaboration","